name: Webprosmeetup
body:
#### Web Professionals Meetup Group This is the Web Professionals Meetup Group (Colorado Springs) git repository for example code and talks. Each meeting has a branch of code If you want to use this repo for your presentation please create a new branch and submit a pull request. Please notify me with your github repository username example: levidehaan submitting a pull request for next meetup session. Existing Meetup Branches:
[js-jq-nodejs](https://github.com/CSNodejs/WebProsMeetup/tree/js-jq-nodejs)
[pcap-map](https://github.com/CSNodejs/WebProsMeetup/tree/pcap-map)
For more information, please see the [wiki](https://github.com/CSNodejs/WebProsMeetup/wiki).
tagline: Repository of code related to the Web Professionals Meetup Group
